        "text": "Another goal: when you're focused on a page, fingers need to be basically a no-op. Even using fingers to turn pages is almost too risky. We want the basic drawing mode to be safe for \"hands all over\", so that you never accidentally invoke some unwanted behaviour due to failed palm rejection or other errant touches.",
